snippet.title: Puffmin Quest - Trailer 2 | Pikmin 2 Mod
snippet.description:
The second trailer for JaySalty's Pikmin 2 mod Puffmin Quest that was originally submitted to Nintendo Fan Game Direct ( NFGD ).

This trailer features new enemies, new puzzle objects, and other new additions to Pikmin 2 never seen before!
